      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas KUNGS\nus Mohſu : tain Wihram buhs\nnokantaim tapt / wiﬀa Draudſe\nlaid winnu ar Akimixeem nomeh-\nta ahran Lehgeka."
