      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Runna us teem Israëka\nBehrneem/ un fakki us teem: Ka\nteem few Puſchkus darriht buhs\nwinnu Drehbju Stuhroß / pee\nwinnu Pehznahfameem/un wee-\nnu paſillu Aukli buhs teem us to\nStuhru Puſchkeem lift."
